ZH: 他在面对困难时从不退缩。
EN: He never retreats when facing difficulties.
ZH: 勇敢的人不会退缩。
EN: Courageous people do not back down.
ZH: 她曾因为失败而退缩过。
EN: She has retreated before due to failure.
ZH: 面对危险，我们不能退缩。
EN: We cannot back down in the face of danger.
ZH: 别人的质疑无法让他退缩。
EN: Others' doubts cannot make him retreat.
ZH: 当他看到挑战时，他毫不退缩。
EN: When he sees a challenge, he does not flinch.
ZH: 面对巨大的压力，她退缩了。
EN: She retreated when faced with enormous pressure.
ZH: 没有人能逼迫他退缩。
EN: No one can force him to back down.
ZH: 我们不能因为困难而退缩。
EN: We cannot retreat because of difficulties.
ZH: 面对困境，她选择退缩。
EN: Faced with adversity, she chose to back down.
ZH: 在生活中我们要勇敢地迈向前方，不退缩。
EN: In life, we must bravely move forward without retreating.
ZH: 走出舒适区是勇敢的人的选择，不退缩。
EN: Stepping out of the comfort zone is the choice of brave people, without retreating.
